{"tid":1088783,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌奶星 馬會又開錯盤 我地曼聯[-0.5/-1] 超高水","createTime":"2019-04-02T09:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T10:18:20.000Z","uid":11254,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4b42fd1dacb54254384ffd6b07b2fb78731982e3","tid":1088783,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:45:25.000Z","msg":"又係咁意分析下啦<br />\n狼隊岩岩FA CUP贏左我地曼年 竟然仲有得受讓 你估馬會開善堂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狼隊要留力星期日打FA CUP 反正英超都無野好爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其次我地SO B 唔係一條濕鳩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會輸比同一隊TWICE<br />\n你以為我地曼年FA CUP 出局係偶然？真係話你on9怕你嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地專登出局，為既就係專心踢英超，前排作客連勝唔撚係偶然，一早plan鳩定晒喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 拉車 連加特 馬斯亞 普巴  加上全能王山齊士<br />\n真係 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n按左層樓落去 聽日又換樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04a34e5c6c4d05b663b1cf10f858a2f1df39d6c","tid":1088783,"uid":64355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"2bbe2afa69694343de3f97f9626cc0ba31b43366","tid":1088783,"uid":138267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:48:05.000Z","msg":"系 我已經約咗經紀睇樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce5735a563830ed1121a57ed6d7ab8d76c93459","tid":1088783,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b04a34e5c6c4d05b663b1cf10f858a2f1df39d6c","tid":1088783,"uid":64355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"g持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:49:07.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"fd9768574f2ce2e7da0414a1207d2f77fcd6f4b9","tid":1088783,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bbe2afa6